OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBorder Force staff to      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstrike over Christmas -    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Funion                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Border Force staff are going on strike 
OL,6, for eight days over Christmas at       
OL,7, Heathrow, Gatwick and several other    
OL,8, airports, the PCS union has announced. 
OL,10,FThousands of other civil servants -    
OL,11,Fincluding driving test examiners - will
OL,12,Falso be taking industrial action.      
OL,14,FPCS General Secretary Mark Serwotka    
OL,15,Fsaid the strikes would "escalate"      
OL,16,Funless the government was prepared "to 
OL,17,Fput money on the table now".           
OL,19,FHe said his members were "skipping     
OL,20,Fmeals" and could not afford heating.   
